### 登录 Alice
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 获取当前用户信息
GET http://localhost:8000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取用户所属家庭列表
GET http://localhost:8000/users/me/families
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取用户 Membership（包含角色）
GET http://localhost:8000/users/me/memberships
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 更新用户信息（昵称 + 电话）
PUT http://localhost:8000/users/me/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "username": "alice",
  "phoneNumber": "1112223333",
  "notes": "更新后的昵称和电话"
}

### 更新密码（需旧密码）
PATCH http://localhost:8000/users/me/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "oldPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newpass456"
}

### 更新密保问题和答案
PUT http://localhost:8000/users/me/reset-question
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "password": "newpass456",
  "securityQuestion": "你最喜欢的饮料？",
  "securityAnswer": "美式咖啡"
}

### 注销账号（逻辑删除）
POST http://localhost:8000/users/me/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reason": "User deleted",
  "confirmed": true
}
